    <li>Typing indicators and read receipts.</li>
    <li>File sharing and document previews.</li>
    <li>Push notifications.</li>
    <li>Message search.</li>
    <li>Encrypted file storage.</li>
    <li>Malware scanning.</li>
    <li>Audit logs and retention policy.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Module 13: Database and Supabase Backend</h2>
  <p class="meta">Owner Type: Backend/Supabase Developer</p>
  <h3>Purpose</h3>
  <p>This is the data foundation for auth, profiles, advocates, posts, consultations, messages, AI queries, reviews, documents, and admin actions.</p>
  <h3 class="green">Prototype / Build Now</h3>
  <ul class="green">
    <li>Tables: profiles, advocates, posts, post_comments, post_reactions, consultation_requests, messages, ai_queries, reviews, admin_actions.</li>
    <li>Supabase Auth.</li>
    <li>Basic Row Level Security.</li>
    <li>Seed demo users and advocates.</li>
    <li>Public read access for verified advocate profiles and public posts.</li>
    <li>Private access for messages and requests.</li>
  </ul>
  <h3 class="red">Later / Full Platform</h3>
  <ul class="red">
    <li>Strict RLS policies.</li>
    <li>Audit logs.</li>
    <li>Storage buckets and signed URLs.</li>
    <li>Retention rules.</li>
    <li>Deletion/export flows.</li>
    <li>Backups.</li>
    <li>Payment, dispute, notification, analytics, and consent tables.</li>
    <li>Security monitoring.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Module 14: Content Moderation, Reporting, and Community Safety</h2>
