    <li>Report post button.</li>
    <li>Report reasons: misinformation, harassment, privacy issue, fake legal advice, spam, abusive content.</li>
    <li>Admin can view reports placeholder/list.</li>
    <li>Admin can hide/remove a post.</li>
    <li>Posting disclaimer: do not share confidential details publicly.</li>
  </ul>
  <h3 class="red">Later / Full Platform</h3>
  <ul class="red">
    <li>Moderation queue.</li>
    <li>Automated toxic content detection.</li>
    <li>Legal misinformation review.</li>
    <li>Repeat offender system.</li>
    <li>Appeal process.</li>
    <li>Sensitive topic labels.</li>
    <li>Fact-check workflow.</li>
    <li>Defamation/privacy escalation process.</li>
    <li>Community guidelines enforcement.</li>
  </ul>

