    <li>Verified consultation-only reviews.</li>
    <li>Review moderation.</li>
    <li>Report review.</li>
    <li>Advocate reply.</li>
    <li>Confidential detail warnings.</li>
    <li>Fake review detection.</li>
    <li>Review dispute workflow.</li>
    <li>Rating breakdown: clarity, professionalism, responsiveness, punctuality.</li>
  </ul>

