  <p class="meta">Owner Type: Backend/Payment Developer</p>
  <h3>Purpose</h3>
  <p>Show how NyayaSetu can become financially sustainable through consultations, subscriptions, and value-added services.</p>
  <h3 class="green">Prototype / Build Now</h3>
